Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:03.98,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Stepped on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:04.81,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,your shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.98,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm "it"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:13.01,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, come here, crabbity crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Step on the crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:15.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Step, step...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:17.99,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,How can we turn Manaka back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:21.64,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,How do you get someone's \Nheart to love someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:23.86,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:28.25,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,If the time comes, it may return, \Nor it may never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:29.50,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:32.68,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, you understand now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.77,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,There are indeed some things in the \Nworld that you cannot do anything about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:41.91,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Stepped on your shadow, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:42.73,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Step!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:51.19,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:54.56,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,There's something my dad \Nwants me to pick up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:57.23,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's at the Fishery Cooperative. \NWill you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:00:58.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:00.49,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:01.92,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:04.00,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Could you watch Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.03,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:07.00,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay! 'Kay, 'kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:40.05,Episode-Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Twenty-Three: \NWho Do These\N Feelings Belong To?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to act all mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:44.55,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:46.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you thought you'd try
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:48.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,to save me from the situation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:49.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.94,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You've been a crybaby lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:57.19,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll be the adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.73,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:04.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we were done \Nwith the Ofunehiki,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,she wanted to tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.78,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:14.37,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering what \Nshe wanted to tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:15.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,she was going to ask Tsumugu out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.30,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.14,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.47,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's more likely that\Nif she says she wants to talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:28.60,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,and it goes that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.43,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,the person Manaka-san would \Nwant to ask out is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:33.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You think it's me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:34.09,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:36.62,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:37.44,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.37,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:47.72,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,"Definitely"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:53.21,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk to everyone \Nabout what Uroko-sama said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:53.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:56.96,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Including Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:00.13,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:03.27,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Because if it were about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:05.42,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I'd want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:08.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:12.26,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's also "definitely"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:16.71,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,The heart to love someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can \Ndo about the sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But with Manaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,we may be able to do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,so I want to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:28.50,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Will thinking about it do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.27,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:35.24,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from trying \Nto find the sea village
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:36.17,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,or trying to wake up Mukaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.69,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:44.30,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,how much damage could the inability \Nto fall in love with someone have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.11,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka looks like she's having fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:50.41,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,and she doesn't seem troubled \Nbecause she lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:54.34,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Chisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.23,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.20,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.68,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I might...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.55,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,actually be a little relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:05.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:10.15,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I think that \Ndepends on the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.61,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.51,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,we can all just solve like we usually do—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.34,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:16.26,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:19.57,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Saying it's better off not having \Nthe ability to love someone... is selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:21.45,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You guys haven't even \Nasked Manaka-san about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.08,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:23.01,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:24.73,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine not knowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.24,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to act all mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:28.26,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a kid, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.61,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.20,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.54,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,there's something wrong with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:37.57,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's really disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.32,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, I'm so annoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.53,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:48.58,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.02,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Loving someone is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:51.89,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,It's better off to be \Nable to love someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:53.19,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:57.38,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Was it okay to leave everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:59.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:01.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, stupid Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.88,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call Kaname stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You said it yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.08,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,It's different when I say it \Nfrom when someone else says it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.35,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I have homework \NI still have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:13.64,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never understand her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.31,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.72,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:21.84,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.54,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-kun wanted to come find you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.86,Danger,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Danger: Do not enter\NTo be demolished soon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.44,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:38.58,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,If Akira's with us, we're \Nnever going to make it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this isn't so bad now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:45.00,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.08,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That shining thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.09,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.74,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on one sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.47,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's from a red-bellied sea slug.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.73,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, how nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.28,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:08.54,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I told the red-bellied sea \Nslug something before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.07,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What did you tell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:10.86,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:13.87,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:16.36,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:18.34,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:20.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:21.93,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:24.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,if you tell the sea slug \Nwhat you're thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.84,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,it'll tell you what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If it spits up a white rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,your wish will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:33.06,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling is true"... wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.58,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,If your feelings are wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.05,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,it'll spit up a black rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:42.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You hold onto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.08,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:45.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you take \Nreally good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.45,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.36,Main,hikri,0000,0000,0000,,That's Manaka's rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:53.64,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Just a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:57.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Its color and shape:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:08:00.72,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,it's flat and looks like \Nit has bad coordination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:02.75,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Rocks have coordination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:07.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka said she told the sea slug \Nsomething but couldn't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,what it was, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.25,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:12.72,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning the thing that \NManaka told the sea slug
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:16.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,has something to do with \Nfalling in love with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.13,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.54,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll just have to ask Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:24.41,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:28.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If the feelings were strong enough \Nfor her to talk to the sea slug,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:30.73,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'll be able to remember them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.63,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If she has the help from \Nthe person she loves,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.73,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,it'll happen for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:36.11,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.12,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:42.60,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,If Manaka's ability to fall in love \Nwith someone does come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.66,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:44.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.55,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.02,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying that \NI can sort of understand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.28,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,what Kaname-san and \NChisaki-san were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:50.80,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:56.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The "if I can't love anyone, \NI won't be sad," thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.89,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You were saying that the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.74,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,or five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.11,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.27,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:08.56,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,263)}If I didn't love them, \NI wouldn't be so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:12.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I don't \Nknow what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:14.70,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Kaname and Chisaki said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.73,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,it might be easier if \Nshe doesn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:23.19,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Watching you guys made me think \Nthat's definitely not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.85,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey! Don't get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:26.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones that showed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:25.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:26.73,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.46,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were able to love Akari,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.08,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Your butt's hanging out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:33.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,this happiness exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:37.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want her to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.40,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,what it feels like to love someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:42.72,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.80,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san, I went \Nahead and took my bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.49,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:04.31,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take one a little later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:05.95,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.73,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:14.21,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I just keep hearing the sound \Nof waves in the back of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:16.05,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.14,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Hii-kun told me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.96,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,to take care of this rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:22.80,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:28.44,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun is trying really \Nhard for me for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:33.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder why he's trying so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.18,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.00,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Since he hasn't told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:44.78,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he has something \Nhe doesn't want to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:47.68,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,This rock is pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:50.82,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,but when I look at it, \NI don't know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:53.10,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,and I feel weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:54.87,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:11:00.74,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san's heart to fall in love \Nwith someone has been taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.34,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,So where her love was,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.95,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,there is now a hole,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.70,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,and it's screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:11.99,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's screaming that it's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.72,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san, that rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.61,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be okay if I borrowed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.49,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.33,Main,mina,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything bad to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.99,Main,mina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it so you can take \Neven better care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:25.70,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Even better care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.48,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.18,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.71,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,On my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.36,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny, Miuna-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.96,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.17,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:42.45,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Now and when you were little, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.86,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari is thinking of Manaka-san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:53.25,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,more than his own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:11:59.78,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.57,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.98,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It's right before exams and \NI'll probably be home late,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.23,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd make \Nextra for dinner, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:09.43,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.93,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you go back to the university,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:13.96,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you eat your vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:16.66,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,When you get so wrapped up in something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.94,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,you forget to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.46,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:23.85,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get sleep, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:27.57,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to just \Nnap on the sofa or the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:29.25,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to \Nrelieve any lethargy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.43,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:34.10,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you didn't need \Nto tell everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.98,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to make a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:39.29,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,about me just going \Nback to the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:40.87,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:43.26,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:44.35,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:49.08,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you feel relieved if you \Ndidn't have the heart to love anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.37,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You're good with your hands, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.25,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.88,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:02.84,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:07.96,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I really wouldn't like losing \Nthe ability to love someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.49,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's one-sided,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.22,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,it's better to have that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:15.52,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:17.30,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,These five years,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.82,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,the reason I studied so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.63,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,the reason I'd cry now and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.13,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,was Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:27.27,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'd be easier if you didn't \Nhave the ability to love someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:31.03,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,but I wouldn't be who I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:32.78,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.22,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.96,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask Kaname out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.04,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:41.54,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how it turns out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:43.41,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if we can't go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:45.66,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can come to terms with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.30,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,This is my own problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:49.80,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.36,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I'm on duty today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:55.25,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I have to write in the log \Nand take it to Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.76,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Her own problem, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:08.96,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.91,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:11.82,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:13.13,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hikari and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.78,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently they already went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.35,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.08,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:20.31,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the sea slug's?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.66,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:26.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like Akari-san's pendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:29.22,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the one with all the shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:33.57,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, all of you helped me with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.62,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:37.41,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:39.58,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,We all helped make it, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.06,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got a ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:47.94,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want to try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:50.24,Emergency Exit,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Exit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.24,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.57,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:54.95,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miuna-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:58.45,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I really can take better care of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:01.03,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose it, and \Nit'll always be with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.39,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Won't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.90,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miuna-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:10.25,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.13,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,it's just you're so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:12.97,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:17.10,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You're so pretty, and nice, and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.06,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You have everything, Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:25.31,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why you \Ncan't lose anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.67,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.44,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:31.88,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:32.76,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.07,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:47.24,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, letting it be in some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:50.87,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I'd take this home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:52.54,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Take it home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:53.84,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.30,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,There are limits to what \Nwe can research here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:58.89,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.80,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:02.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What about Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:03.27,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:06.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait until she gets her feelings back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:10.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She's in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:14.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do whatever I can to \Nget her ability to love back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:17.75,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If you were able to \Nstimulate her feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:19.98,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Stimulate her feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.53,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:22.30,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.52,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Like take her on a date, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:29.53,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss her and hold her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:31.80,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a pervert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:35.97,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don't feel \Nthat way toward Mukaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You can just act like you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.72,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine even if it's just a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.77,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.64,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,that it's me that Mukaido \Nis in love with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,When she looks at you, \Nshe gets all red in the face
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:51.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and says your name all sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:54.11,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,And that's proof that she loves me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.24,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to doubt \NManaka's feelings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:03.67,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:07.56,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,My height and my arm strength \Nare five years beyond yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.29,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.13,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Please give up, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.52,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:27.44,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,especially if Mukaido does love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to say that you love her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka might turn back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:35.58,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.96,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,the feelings of love for someone \Nshould never be messed around with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.70,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm in love with Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:44.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.72,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.39,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:00.85,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:06.46,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:12.52,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:16.15,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But if I lose her now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:36.41,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:40.24,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a nostalgic voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.05,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Mukaido's Ena...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:45.81,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:51.71,Italics,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,So many feelings are \Nwithin these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:56.86,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even have Ena... \Nwhat the hell is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:58.86,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:14.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:15.70,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:19.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're able to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:33.48,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what it \Nfeels like to have Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.72,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.59,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.35,Main,fish,0000,0000,0000,,Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:51.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:57.03,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but will you let \Nme go alone from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.09,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? By yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But you've never been to the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:05.15,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to face Chisaki properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:08.43,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I can't move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:10.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:11.55,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.74,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.45,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:22.56,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared to be alone in Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:27.41,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:40.00,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tsumugu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:42.72,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,H-How...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:44.55,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you in Shishio, Tsumugu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:46.57,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I came after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.15,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:49.51,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You can breathe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:50.43,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:53.70,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Ena?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:58.68,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,My parents hated the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:01.66,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,They left behind Gramps,\Nwho wanted to stay by the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:02.94,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,and went to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:06.69,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to stay with Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.21,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to stay by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:10.95,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:12.29,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:17.83,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,when Hikari mistakenly thought that \NEgawa and the others broke the Ojoshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.33,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:22.57,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That time, you found out the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:25.09,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,and tried to defend Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.84,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(259,1)}Because if everyone else\Nfinds out about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:30.48,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe how \Nfoolish you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.94,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hikari will end up the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:36.19,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,To think that people can become \Nso pathetic for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.10,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You're always so quiet and calm,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:44.34,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,and yet sometimes you become so \Nfierce that I can't handle you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:47.85,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:52.32,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,thought you were like the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.21,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you like, Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:32.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:33.07,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.06,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Was I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:34.73,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Why just after five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:35.76,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting like the tragic heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:35.98,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,This is a talk between guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:36.85,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:37.44,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:37.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This is messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:39.88,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Something I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.14,Episode-Title - Copy,ep title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Twenty-Four:\NDetritus
